Package com.epam.dataaccess.dao.mariadb.impl

Class MariaDBConstants

java.lang.Object
com.epam.dataaccess.dao.mariadb.impl.MariaDBConstants
public final class MariaDBConstants extends Object
Class which contains various constants used in a database application. The class contains constant strings representing names of database tables and columns, as well as prepared SQL statements. The class has a private constructor to prevent creating instances of it and all the fields are declared public static final which makes them usable as constants throughout the code. The constants are used to define database table names, columns, and queries.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Hrebenozhko Ruslan
